{"tid":1670204,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"巴絲們，請回想活動初衷。","createTime":"2019-10-23T02:18:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T06:28:12.000Z","uid":160136,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"53bf84fbdcf84dd59cf9712f1577460d478374a0","tid":1670204,"uid":160136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:18:33.000Z","msg":"最近見到連登每日都好多意見，總覺得有人分裂緊連登。<br />\n連我自己都開始漸漸忘記當初想要嘅野，當然五大訴求依然識嗌，但背出嚟又喺咪完整？<br />\n<br />\n無論是否風向定還是真心嘅爭論，想大家記得五大訴求，缺一不可唔單單是口號，諗吓我哋為支線，為支線嘅支線或者支線嘅支線嘅支線鬧到面紅耳赤又是否幫助到五大訴求？<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求仲識唔識背？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lwf7uFV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLwf7uFV.jpg&h=11eaf1bf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/34PoNsB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F34PoNsB.jpg&h=987b676f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家靜下心來，背一次五大訴求，到底爭取緊咩，自己應該要做咩，做自己覺得岩嘅野，我哋好難先行到呢一步，千萬唔好亂，我哋唔係well-trained，但我地香港人最叻係識進步同學習，大家加油。"},{"pid":"1a50b7a70f0e104b6c2eb1779e4e60521e5fc09b","tid":1670204,"uid":265168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:34:15.000Z","msg":"我見到大家咁樣嗌交我真係有啲心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><br />\n食住個勢 connect全世界<br />\n求搞手<br />\n求下各位推行動po</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n[擴大戰線] [行動] 與其嘈加泰集會 不如唔搞呢個<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1668190\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1668190</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><br />\n食住個勢 connect全世界<br />\n求搞手<br />\n求下各位推行動po</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n[擴大戰線] [行動] 與其嘈加泰集會 不如唔搞呢個<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1668190\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1668190</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><br />\n食